# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Live credential files — NEVER tracked.
#
# These are created by the operator by copying the .example versions, and they
# hold real secrets: TURN credentials in .env, and HA1 password hashes in
# config/users.conf. They were tracked until 2026-07; that meant every
# deployment accumulated real credentials in a file git considered part of
# THIS PUBLIC REPO, one `git commit -a && git push` away from publication.
#
# Do not remove these ignores. Do not `git add -f` these paths.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
.env
config/users.conf
